&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;    Args:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      inputs: A `Tensor` with type `int32` or `int64` containing the ids&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;         to be looked up in `lookup table`.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      vocab_size: An int. Vocabulary size.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      num_units: An int. Number of embedding hidden units.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      zero_pad: A boolean. If True, all the values of the fist row (id 0)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;        should be constant zeros.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      scale: A boolean. If True. the outputs is multiplied by sqrt num_units.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      scope: Optional scope for `variable_scope`.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      reuse: Boolean, whether to reuse the weights of a previous layer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;        by the same name.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;    Returns:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;      A `Tens